F-FUSION-ATTN-ROOFLINE -- round 7 of the GPU sec10 GEMM-fusion (attention) axis
================================================================================
DATE: 2026-05-25
GOAL: port the N204 roofline-GEMM toolkit into the fused softmax(QK^T/sqrt(d))V
      inner GEMMs and measure how close it gets to the cuBLAS-TC ceiling.

KEY INSIGHT (acted on): hexa ALREADY hits the GEMM roofline standalone -- N204
"TMA SWIZZLE_128B" reached cuBLAS 0.978 parity @ M=8192 (PRs #333/#335). The
fused flash-attention lost its wall (round-5 best 3.47x slower) NOT because hexa
can't do roofline GEMM, but because the fused kernel's inner QK^T and P.V GEMMs
were naive (single-warp, small 16x16 wmma tiles, no TMA, no double-buffer, no
swizzle). This round transplants the proven N204 toolkit into the fused kernel.

