MMA FRAGMENT-MAP DISCOVERY CAMPAIGN (cheap 16x16 probes, $0):
  probe1 (mma_probe.cu): naive trans=K^T / non-trans=V assumption -- both MISMATCH
  probe2 (probe2.cu, disambiguating): non-trans + mma.row.col => C = A . B^T (err 1e-7 MATCH)
